function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Donan_Tomb_End")[1]
	idDonanLocDungeon = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Donan_Tomb_EndLoc")[1]
	
	--Move and Fade Donan
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(idDonanTomb, "")
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT, CONVO_DONAN_WAIT_01)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT, CONVO_DONAN_WAIT_02)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT, CONVO_DONAN_WAIT_03)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT, S_CONVO_DONAN_06)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT, idDonanLocDungeon, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_DONAN_DUNGEON_EXIT, 1)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idDonanTomb = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Donan_Tomb_End")[1]
	idDonanFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_DONAN_FOLLOWER)	
	
	-- Donan move action
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idActor)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActor, idDonanTomb, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActor, idDonanTomb)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idActor, "ARRIVED")
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idDonanTomb)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	--Disable Door + Enables Door Monster
	tDoor = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_ZakfortKeep_Dungeon_Door_Monster")
	for i, idDoor in ipairs(tDoor) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idDoor, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idDoor, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)
	end
end

function Start()
	
	idDonanTomb = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Donan_Tomb_End")[1]
	idRitualFX = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_ZakFortKeep_RitualFX")[1]
	
	--Donan begins Ritual 
	--Hydra.Wait(1.4)
	Hydra.ActorFaceActor(idDonanTomb, idRitualFX) 
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idDonanTomb, ANIM_DONAN_USE)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idDonanTomb, FX_SOULSTONE_INTRO)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idDonanTomb)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idRitualFX)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idDonanTomb, idRitualFX, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric", true, "HP_Portrait", "HP_Mouth")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idDonanTomb, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric", true)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idDonanTomb, 0.5)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONVO_DONAN_11, idDonanTomb)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idDonanTomb, S_CONVO_DONAN_11)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idDonanTomb, 0.5)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idDonanTomb)
		
	--Donan fails Ritual
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idDonanTomb, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idDonanTomb, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric")
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(idDonanTomb, SNO_EXPLOSION_FX)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idRitualFX)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idDonanTomb, FX_SOULSTONE_OUTRO)	
	
	--Donan reacts to failing Ritual
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idDonanTomb, ANIM_DONAN_WOUNDED, false, false)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_DONAN_EXPLODE, idDonanTomb)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idDonanTomb, CONVO_DONAN_EXPLODE)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idDonanTomb, 1)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idDonanTomb)

	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idDonanTomb, "QST_VERGE1_ADVANCE")
	
end
